{"tid":482484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(警黑又犯罪)警長偷拍裙底春斷正 受害人竟然係警嫂","createTime":"2017-11-28T07:52:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T10:19:57.000Z","uid":14918,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3966be56827c447f299886a831e2181d3e3055f5","tid":482484,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T07:52:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171128/large/1511853876_4f95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171128%2Flarge%2F1511853876_4f95.jpg&h=14cc6e68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名休班警長涉嫌在商場偷拍女子裙底春，昨日當場斷正被捕，而受害女子據悉為一名警員的妻子。事發昨午5時許，一名男子在油塘大本型商場乘搭扶手電梯時，以手機偷拍前方一名女子的裙底，當場被人揭發捉個正著，警員接報到場，以涉嫌游蕩將偷拍男子拘捕，帶返觀塘警署扣查。消息指，被捕男子為一名警長，而受害女子則為一名警員的妻子。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》昨日已就是否有警務人員涉及偷拍事宜向警方查詢，但一直未獲得回覆。<br />\n<br />\n你敢爆，我敢獎！ 即Call《蘋果》24小時爆相爆片熱線 ：63836568"},{"pid":"f2619f856f4b614ef4d4b92df1f5d66522ab7a46","tid":482484,"uid":17631,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T07:59:24.000Z","msg":"香港警察+1分 朋友妻咪走雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4efac4a18f1a241d0e6ee166007a8307bf28b85a","tid":482484,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T08:00:25.000Z","msg":"以為台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5534ec6d9212ff9488757aca966fdbb61597ca7","tid":482484,"uid":22858,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T08:01:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>黑警：勾二嫂姐，唔算害群之馬</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd1f7707a02a265a0a18011bdf04eb8ce0